**Simulated Problem**




Title: Classroom Performance Analysis

Description: Simulate the marks of 50 students in 5 different subjects. Assume marks follow a normal distribution with varying means and standard deviations for each subject. Identify the top 5% of students by average marks and compare their variance in performance to the bottom 5%.

